{"tid":2513832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共滲透英國學府　港生聲援反修例遭內地生糾眾欺凌威嚇起底　校方坐視不理","createTime":"2021-05-03T00:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T01:06:21.000Z","uid":271829,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ea0ab91180d9c42bb37b92f12100f32511bed8","tid":2513832,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pcj4VONsZtUiAF0KqHlzGAY1kXw=/535x325/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2REALNNCXBETNOZQEX2NLUYLA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fpcj4VONsZtUiAF0KqHlzGAY1kXw%3D%2F535x325%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2REALNNCXBETNOZQEX2NLUYLA4.jpg&h=5882946e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留學英國的港人Jamie（左）和Kitty（右）現身說法在英國校園中舉辦聲援港人活動時遭內地生糾眾騷擾，校方亦指令她們中止相關活動，認為因中共的滲透令英國校園的言論自由遭損害。譚志輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lkwIrFLJOu04hYCuWB3TS_hmx-U=/535x330/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XOS2BDAZVZHF3BA5DWW6YQ3SJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlkwIrFLJOu04hYCuWB3TS_hmx-U%3D%2F535x330%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXOS2BDAZVZHF3BA5DWW6YQ3SJU.jpg&h=f73200e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKitty因在校內舉辦聲援港人活動，險被內地生襲擊，事後被起底，全名遭放上內地網。Kitty向校方求助，一度被無視。譚志輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0G3120IzZHnZFm5zcGsLHfQXc_Q=/535x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7KFL66NE4RC3RPA45YFCVSHCFY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0G3120IzZHnZFm5zcGsLHfQXc_Q%3D%2F535x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7KFL66NE4RC3RPA45YFCVSHCFY.JPG&h=1f955a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全英中國學生學者聯誼會（CSSAUK）據其網站所稱是「受中華人民共和國駐英國大使館教育處支持」，更號稱是目前英國最大的華人社團。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v4C-lShH3pB0y_WyoS0WnwfKc-g=/535x1158/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GWLQJ2NGKFEZJMTAZ5OFMHLPZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv4C-lShH3pB0y_WyoS0WnwfKc-g%3D%2F535x1158%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGWLQJ2NGKFEZJMTAZ5OFMHLPZY.jpg&h=f47b0ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有留學生透露中共透過其駐英使館支持的組織全英中國學生學者聯誼會（CSSAUK）滲透英國大學，會使用「發紅包」等手段去動員內地生投票選出指定候選人當選為學生會委員，被指是赤裸裸的賂選。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n內地生揮五星旗闖港生集會 辱罵「漢奸」「曱甴」搶文宣<br />\n在倫敦一所羅素集團的名校就讀的Kitty（化名）亦有類似遭遇，她前年10月1日在校內與幾位港人學生即興發起Stand with HK集會，邀請所有支持香港人的學生參與，當時出席的有十數個香港和本地學生，各人手持自製文宣及高叫支持香港的口號，未幾即有內地生到場，用普通話指罵他們是「曱甴」、「漢奸」等：「我還記得他們當中有人揮動反轉了的五星紅旗，當場有種很滑稽的感覺。」<br />\n但隨着對方糾眾漸多近百，氣氛亦開始緊張，保安即時介入並分開兩團人，並要求Kitty等人離開，「但明明我們甚麼都沒做，只是坐着並喊口號，是他們來騷擾我們，為何不是要求他們離開？」<br />\nKitty當時手持自製的反修例運動時序表，「突然有個臉容十分兇悍的內地生閃出到我身前，瞪着我的時序表，之後對我怒目相向，發難一手扯下我的文宣丟在地上。」保安即時將涉事人帶走，並又再要求Kitty等人先行離去，Kitty一夥擔心情況會失控，只好屈服。<br />\n<br />\n遭起底個人資料現內地網 港生獲批集會條件：不能發出聲音<br />\n事後與Kitty同住的內地生友人發現，Kitty和其身旁的同伴均被起底，將全名發佈在內地的社交群組並指她們是「港獨分子」、「曱甴」等。<br />\nKitty相當擔心，並多次向校方委派負責照顧她學業以外問題的導師發電郵求助，但都如泥牛入海。直至Kitty到其辦公室要求面談，才獲告知他不懂得如何處理，並轉介她予一位高級導師，「他態度比之前的積極得多，也開解了我，不過也無法解決。最令我失望的是，就是在校園發表意見竟變得如此不安全。」<br />\n事實上，Kitty等人在事件後再向校方申請聲援港人的活動都屢遭拖延，最後獲有條件批准，「條件是我們不能發出聲音，這令我意識到在校內其實我們已無甚空間去就香港議題發聲。」Kitty直指校方是「買中共怕」 :「因為怕冇咗內地生學費。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/SEQIBJGFCRGHLO2S7TMMYJAJUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FSEQIBJGFCRGHLO2S7TMMYJAJUE%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtRjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=84af5a8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FSEQIBJGFCRGHLO2S7TMMYJAJUE%2F&h=b03d1bdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/SEQIBJGFCRGHLO2S7TMMYJAJUE/</a>"},{"pid":"fd3eb4c661ce00965f5e107b90230fe64340d9e3","tid":2513832,"uid":342828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:42:08.000Z","msg":"一日中共仲喺度，去邊都會俾佢攪，火星都唔例外。"},{"pid":"9eebf69aab4b19db9b9e3c28f2c1104676ee9ec6","tid":2513832,"uid":26014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:49:25.000Z","msg":"英國議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263e8dca473656c0409adba4d1a643192f2781c9","tid":2513832,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:55:21.000Z","msg":"香港人條腰骨可唔可以唔好咁軟。<br />\n俾人打 就打撚返人啦。<br />\n大不了 兩邊都入廠。<br />\n對面係海外讀得書一定係支那富二代既金叵羅啦。<br />\n打撚柒佢地 睇下仲夠唔夠膽。"},{"pid":"2b97eab1c70dfb2d7658b1887b7af98b6670f85a","tid":2513832,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"263e8dca473656c0409adba4d1a643192f2781c9","tid":2513832,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:55:21.000Z","msg":"香港人條腰骨可唔可以唔好咁軟。<br />\n俾人打 就打撚返人啦。<br />\n大不了 兩邊都入廠。<br />\n對面係海外讀得書一定係支那富二代既金叵羅啦。<br />\n打撚柒佢地 睇下仲夠唔夠膽。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:55:49.000Z","msg":"1換4 換撚到佢地驚"},{"pid":"e6ac8b0d0ef09d2a1c00da4ffc2c2065c194598a","tid":2513832,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:56:00.000Z","msg":"Pudh"},{"pid":"f98dc5af6e73d616d03dbfe87b3814a6ed3eb956","tid":2513832,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"263e8dca473656c0409adba4d1a643192f2781c9","tid":2513832,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:55:21.000Z","msg":"香港人條腰骨可唔可以唔好咁軟。<br />\n俾人打 就打撚返人啦。<br />\n大不了 兩邊都入廠。<br />\n對面係海外讀得書一定係支那富二代既金叵羅啦。<br />\n打撚柒佢地 睇下仲夠唔夠膽。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"而家又成個cry baby咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f4a0f85096fae8